## Package: ibexa/admin-ui
Core Back Office interface bundle for Ibexa DXP (Digital Experience Platform).

## Key Commands:
```bash
# PHP
composer fix-cs          # Auto-fix PHP code style
composer test            # Run all tests

# JavaScript/TypeScript
yarn test                # Run all checks
yarn fix                 # Auto-fix frontend issues

# Frontend Assets (from project root)
yarn ibexa:dev           # Development build
yarn ibexa:build         # Production build
```

## Testing:
```bash
./vendor/bin/phpunit -c phpunit.xml tests/lib/
./vendor/bin/phpunit -c phpunit.integration.xml tests/integration/
```

## Code Style:
- PHP: `declare(strict_types=1)` required
- PHPStan level 8
- Frontend: Prettier + ESLint via `@ibexa/eslint-config`
